12:05.531 --> 12:10.068
Get me my daughter back,
and I'll give you Latif.

12:12.037 --> 12:15.339
<i>My name is Clare Somersby,</i>
<i>and I am an aid worker.</i>

12:15.373 --> 12:17.008
<i>And I am here to</i>
<i>heal people...</i>

12:23.616 --> 12:26.151
