15:06.946 --> 15:10.081
This is gris-gris.

15:11.017 --> 15:14.486
Yes. He gave them to me.

15:18.557 --> 15:20.058
I will take them.
No.

15:20.092 --> 15:21.125
Clare...

15:27.332 --> 15:31.236
I will give them to you.
As a gift. To keep you safe.

15:33.405 --> 15:36.708
I have enough protection,

15:36.742 --> 15:42.147
not least in the shipment of
arms your father is sending me

15:42.181 --> 15:46.484
to ensure you return unharmed.

15:49.989 --> 15:53.792
When the guns arrive,
you will be released.

15:53.826 --> 15:59.964
But until then, you will earn your
food and water by treating my men.

15:59.998 --> 16:02.300
We will. Thank you.

16:06.205 --> 16:08.773
I need only one doctor.

16:10.543 --> 16:13.311
No! No, Bakri!

16:13.346 --> 16:16.448
Bakri!
No, sweetheart!

16:16.482 --> 16:17.782
Subin!

16:17.817 --> 16:21.719
