friend.  <i>As-salaam alaikum.</i>

18:14.464 --> 18:18.133
<i>Alaikum salaam.</i> Mr. Sinclair,
Mr. Stonebridge,

18:18.902 --> 18:21.070
Matak Achmed.

18:21.138 --> 18:25.442
