need a bigger case.

19:01.744 --> 19:03.146
Is it Special Ops?

19:03.171 --> 19:05.848
You going to render Bashir?
Make him stand trial for war crimes?

19:05.849 --> 19:07.316
Snatch the President
of Sudan?

19:07.350 --> 19:10.418
Well, why not? He's already
been indicted by the courts.

19:10.453 --> 19:12.821
