19:34.676 --> 19:37.311
Wasn't Iraq, was it? Kosovo?

19:39.380 --> 19:41.348
The snake guy's a
Russian called Grigor.

19:41.382 --> 19:42.649
Right. Where'd
you take these?

19:42.684 --> 19:45.252
Some shebeen, not
far from here.

19:45.287 --> 19:47.021
You want to tell
me where it is?

19:47.055 --> 19:49.491
Quid pro quo.

19:49.525 --> 19:52.661
Who are those guys you were with?
What was in those cases?

19:52.695 --> 19:53.929
Heh.

19:53.964 --> 19:55.698
Hey, what did
you just do?

19:57.034 --> 19:58.568
Well, I'm going to find
out who that guy is,

19:58.602 --> 20:01.204
