and you know it.

20:13.684 --> 20:16.052
Hey, I got a driver.

20:17.188 --> 20:17.954
Awesome.

20:17.988 --> 20:19.322
Jacoub!

20:19.356 --> 20:22.993
Hey hottie, it's me. We
good to talk dirty again?

20:23.027 --> 20:24.828
Yes, the line is secure.

20:24.862 --> 20:26.563
