if you don't.

20:44.315 --> 20:46.449
My name is Jacoub.
You are American also, yes?

20:46.483 --> 20:49.118
I have made arrangements
for the exchange.

20:49.153 --> 20:52.188
We are meeting them
at noon tomorrow.

20:52.222 --> 20:54.089
