23:20.408 --> 23:22.309
Oh, shit, that's him!

23:23.878 --> 23:24.712
<i>I have an</i>
<i>ID on that photo.</i>

23:26.214 --> 23:29.116
The man's name is Andre Botha.

23:29.150 --> 23:30.771
He's a South African mercenary

23:30.796 --> 23:31.996
