private security firm.

23:34.222 --> 23:35.322
He's been playing
us all along.

23:38.260 --> 23:39.293
No shit.

23:43.298 --> 23:44.565
We gotta follow him.
Let's go. Okay.

23:44.599 --> 23:46.134
Uh-uh. Not yet.

23:47.503 --> 23:49.537
Jacoub, get out.
I'm driving.

23:49.571 --> 23:51.405
Not until you tell me
what this is all about.

23:51.440 --> 23:53.207
Maggie, not now. I'll tell
you while I'm driving.

23:53.241 --> 23:54.708
Jacoub, get out
of the car.

23:54.742 --> 23:56.109
No! What's in it for me?

23:57.946 --> 23:59.079
You better
talk fast.

23:59.113 --> 24:01.048
Get out of
the fucking car.

24:01.082 --> 24:02.616
Oh, you've got to
be kidding me.

24:02.651 --> 24:03.984
This is my car!

24:04.019 --> 24:05.953
So get in.

24:05.987 --> 24:08.022
You are such a piece
of work, you know that?

24:08.089 --> 24:09.189
Maggie, not now.

24:12.794 --> 24:16.162
Yeah, we've been compromised.
We need to extract the principal.

24:16.196 --> 24:19.098
No, we can't risk them
aborting the exchange.

24:19.132 --> 24:21.400
I've got a tail to shake,
I'll see you later. Out.

24:24.572 --> 24:25.905
Shit.

24:25.940 --> 24:27.141
He's made us.

24:33.848 --> 24:35.883
You couldn't just do what
I say, could you?

24:35.918 --> 24:37.985
Always gotta put the squeeze on, and
try and get something for yourself.

24:38.020 --> 24:39.421
Sound familiar?

24:39.455 --> 24:41.356
If we lose him, I'm never
gonna sleep with you again.

24:41.390 --> 24:42.424
Ever!

24:42.458 --> 24:44.292
Like I'd miss those
three seconds.

24:46.929 --> 24:47.963
What is happening?

24:47.997 --> 24:50.098
Plan B. Buckle up.

24:57.139 --> 24:58.773
He was there,
man, I'm telling you.

24:58.807 --> 25:01.143
That fucking man from the
shipyard is tailing us.

25:05.248 --> 25:06.615
Fucker.

25:08.886 --> 25:10.620
I see them!

25:10.654 --> 25:11.688
I see!
Yeah, I got 'em.

25:14.125 --> 25:15.526
Where the fuck's he
gone? Do you see him?

25:15.560 --> 25:16.761
Negative.

25:19.498 --> 25:20.598
You wanna hold on?

25:26.472 --> 25:27.638
Fuck!

25:43.190 --> 25:44.223
That hurt?

25:48.964 --> 25:50.197
What do you got here, huh?

25:51.600 --> 25:54.602
Fuck me. You guys are
tooled up for a war!

25:56.138 --> 25:57.472
Yeah.

25:57.506 --> 26:00.074
All right. Thank
you very much.

26:01.543 --> 26:02.577
You all right?

26:02.611 --> 26:04.545
You fucking son
of a bitch!

26:04.580 --> 26:05.446
Yeah, you sound fine.

26:05.480 --> 26:06.881
You?

26:06.915 --> 26:07.948
My car!
Yeah, yeah, yeah,

26:07.983 --> 26:09.516
I'll buy you a new one.
My car!

26:09.550 --> 26:13.219
You! Get out of the car.
Get out of the fucking car right now!

26:13.253 --> 26:14.720
Leave it.

26:20.861 --> 26:21.628
Get in the car.
Get in the car!

26:21.662 --> 26:23.230
Jacoub, get in!

26:39.583 --> 26:43.252
I've taken two of 'em out.
I got their weapons, but I'm t.

26:43.287 --> 26:47.624
That guy in the photo with the snake
tattoo is a Russian called Grigor?

26:47.658 --> 26:50.193
He's a Chechen.
Grigor Tchevsky.

26:50.227 --> 26:52.896
We're cross-referencing
border controls.

26:52.930 --> 26:55.365
Andre Botha, Grigor Tchevsky,

26:55.399 --> 26:57.634
<i>and a third mercenary,</i>
<i>Casper Bryce.</i>

26:57.668 --> 27:00.236
<i>They all flew into Khartoum on</i>
<i>the same flight two days ago.</i>

27:00.271 --> 27:02.472
We're sending the information
to Stonebridge now.

27:02.506 --> 27:03.439
Major.

27:03.474 --> 27:05.308
Room service.

27:06.911 --> 27:08.278
We haven't ordered anything.

27:08.312 --> 27:11.414
It's for Mr. Crawford.
Compliments of the hotel.

27:11.449 --> 27:13.350
Why don't you leave it outside,
we'll collect it later.

27:16.054 --> 27:17.388
He needs to sign for it.

27:18.957 --> 27:20.191
Just a moment.

27:21.593 --> 27:23.561
Shut
the door for him.

27:29.969 --> 27:32.971
There's one other man,
just off to the side. Get ready.

27:33.005 --> 27:34.373
What are you going to use?

27:34.407 --> 27:35.374
They brought it with them.

27:35.408 --> 27:37.075
Okay.

27:37.109 --> 27:39.177
Hi, come in. Come on in.

27:56.295 --> 27:57.328
Nice work.

28:09.775 --> 28:12.310
You really should pay your driver more.
This place is a hovel.

28:13.612 --> 28:15.314
I have to deliver these.

28:17.383 --> 28:18.550
Sorry, buddy.

28:19.652 --> 28:20.652
I know it's your home.

28:21.521 --> 28:23.221
This is just a room.

28:24.424 --> 28:25.490
They were my home.

28:32.866 --> 28:35.101
Janjaweed.

28:35.136 --> 28:37.203
He had a farm, once.

28:38.172 --> 28:39.739
They destroyed that, too.

28:45.379 --> 28:47.147
Quite a gash you
got on your head.

28:49.150 --> 28:50.383
Let me have a
look at that.

28:52.553 --> 28:54.521
Oh, yeah.

29:53.411 --> 29:58.080
When I found out Clare was working
in Sudan I approached Matak,

29:58.115 --> 30:01.250
and bribed him to have
her visa revoked.

30:01.285 --> 30:03.119
Instead he had her abducted.

30:04.255 --> 30:06.323
He played distraught,
of course.

30:06.357 --> 30:08.321
Promised to personally
liaise with the Janjaweed

30:08.346 --> 30:09.973
to broker the deal
to get her back.

30:10.429 --> 30:11.462
For a fee.

30:14.334 --> 30:16.368
So, you see, if I hadn't made
him aware of her value,

30:20.974 --> 30:22.692
I couldn't trust that
they'd deliver her to me

30:22.717 --> 30:24.217
even once they had the weapons,

30:24.244 --> 30:26.813
so I had Dieter prepare
a covert team to

30:26.838 --> 30:29.084
plan to be at the
exchange just in case.

30:29.182 --> 30:31.650
They were in place
before my arrest.

30:31.685 --> 30:34.620
What they've done since is without
my knowledge or guidance.

30:37.591 --> 30:39.124
How many others are
on the team?

30:42.362 --> 30:45.298
Two more. Dieter and Andre.

30:49.303 --> 30:51.103
They've both been
taken out.

30:54.741 --> 30:57.142
Then Clare's in
your hands now.

31:01.481 --> 31:02.781
<i>My whole life,</i>

31:04.617 --> 31:08.119
everything I have done has
been a "fuck you" to his wars,

31:08.153 --> 31:10.354
and the blood money he's
made from fueling them.

31:13.124 --> 31:15.558
And now he's
using it all to save me.

31:17.594 --> 31:19.729
Well that is not saving me.

31:21.599 --> 31:23.266
Not like that.

31:25.136 --> 31:26.837
Please, not like that.

32:14.355 --> 32:17.424
That man that you murdered,
where are they taking him?

32:17.458 --> 32:19.359
To a wadi near here.

32:19.394 --> 32:21.161
It is almost full.

32:22.463 --> 32:25.498
But there is still room
for a few more bodies.

32:25.533 --> 32:27.466
He's my fiance.

32:27.501 --> 32:29.568
I want to give him
a proper burial.

32:31.238 --> 32:35.140
And what will you
give me in return?

32:35.174 --> 32:37.308
Nothing you can't take.

32:44.651 --> 32:46.118
Colonel, it's Sinclair.

32:46.152 --> 32:48.387
<i>I think we should abort.</i>
<i>We're too exposed.</i>

32:48.421 --> 32:50.623
What about Stonebridge?

32:50.657 --> 32:53.159
He wants to continue. But I'm convinced
Crawford's double-crossing us.

32:53.194 --> 32:56.330
<i>We have no idea how many more</i>
<i>of these guys are out there.</i>

32:56.364 --> 32:58.465
All right. Stonebridge
knows what he's doing.

32:58.500 --> 33:00.167
<i>And we need that</i>
<i>intel on Latif.</i>

33:00.202 --> 33:02.369
Where's Scott?

33:02.404 --> 33:04.405
Gathering intelligence,
apparently.

33:04.439 --> 33:07.308
<i>He said he'll meet us</i>
<i>at the exchange.</i>

33:07.342 --> 33:08.909
Well, make sure
he gets there.

33:08.944 --> 33:11.178
It's Scott's job to
watch your back.

33:13.515 --> 33:15.916
Lucky me.

33:15.951 --> 33:18.652
Maggie, I said no.
It's too dangerous.

33:18.686 --> 33:20.879
Bullshit!
The arms dealer's daughter?

33:20.904 --> 33:22.704
That's like my
Pulitzer Prize right there!

33:22.723 --> 33:24.591
I said no!

33:24.625 --> 33:26.159
And I still think there's
more you're not telling me!

33:29.596 --> 33:30.730
Where's the car?

33:32.966 --> 33:34.533
Which car?

33:34.568 --> 33:36.468
The fuckin' car we
stole. Where is it?

33:37.804 --> 33:38.971
I took it back.

33:39.005 --> 33:40.473
You fucking kidding me?

33:40.507 --> 33:44.010
His driving license was
inside. With his address.

33:44.044 --> 33:45.452
I didn't know you
still wanted it.

33:45.453 --> 33:46.553
Of course I still want it!

33:46.554 --> 33:48.911
If I don't get to that exchange
point, people are gonna die.

33:49.084 --> 33:50.518
You understand that?

33:50.552 --> 33:52.420
Okay, so we'll just steal
another one, okay?

33:52.454 --> 33:55.657
Where from? The only transport
around here is a fuckin' goat!

33:55.692 --> 33:58.594
My neighbor has a car.
He will lend it to you, I promise.

33:58.628 --> 34:01.063
Come with me, and
show me, right now.

34:03.299 --> 34:04.799
You call this
piece of shit a car?

34:06.268 --> 34:07.468
Fuck.

34:20.380 --> 34:21.480
How long till we get there?

34:23.083 --> 34:25.217
Soon. Relax.

34:25.252 --> 34:27.418
Everything is prepared,

34:27.454 --> 34:29.054
is it not?

34:29.089 --> 34:30.289
Everything's prepared.

34:35.228 --> 34:37.030
Stonebridge?
We have new intelligence.

34:37.063 --> 34:39.699
We're cross-referencing
border controls.

34:39.734 --> 34:43.335
Another three of Crawford's men
arrived in Sudan yesterday.

34:43.371 --> 34:45.371
<i>Looks like you're</i>
<i>gonna have company.</i>

34:45.406 --> 34:46.606
All right.

34:47.208 --> 34:48.341
Problem?

34:48.375 --> 34:49.775
No.

35:40.295 --> 35:42.530
I have a visual
on the boss.

35:42.564 --> 35:44.401
<i>As soon as he</i>
<i>has his daughter, we take</i>

35:44.426 --> 35:45.845
<i>out the special forces.</i>

35:45.935 --> 35:47.269
Roger that.

36:32.584 --> 36:33.550
We spotted anyone?

36:35.653 --> 36:36.653
That abandoned bus.

36:37.589 --> 36:38.789
The barn.

36:41.293 --> 36:42.293
Maybe the walkway.

36:46.030 --> 36:47.231
I don't see anyone.

36:49.067 --> 36:50.601
Neither can I, but that's
where I'd put men.

36:52.270 --> 36:55.071
So what's my role? Apart
from sitting duck?

36:55.105 --> 36:57.373
You grab the girl. She'll
make a perfect shield.

36:57.408 --> 36:59.575
No one's going to shoot
you with her in the way.

36:59.610 --> 37:02.145
Doesn't sound
very chivalrous.

37:02.180 --> 37:04.014
But I like it.
Yeah, good plan.

37:05.049 --> 37:06.616
Where the fuck
are you, Scott?

37:12.824 --> 37:14.693
If you don't hurry up, you're
gonna miss the party.

37:54.333 --> 37:55.300
Crawford...

37:55.901 --> 37:57.068
Clare?

37:59.171 --> 38:00.171
Clare!

38:03.008 --> 38:05.276
It's okay. You're
gonna be fine.

38:08.514 --> 38:10.215
I'm gonna bring you
home with me.

38:22.362 --> 38:26.632
And the trucks? The shipment
of arms that you promised?

38:27.701 --> 38:28.834
Where are they?

38:29.569 --> 38:30.569
They're coming.

38:33.406 --> 38:35.307
When I have my daughter.

38:40.545 --> 38:42.780
Show me them. Now.

38:45.983 --> 38:50.487
He will bring them soon! And
offers this as collateral!

38:56.492 --> 38:57.592
Jacoub,
you got this?

38:57.626 --> 38:59.427
Hold this.
Sure.

39:09.071 --> 39:12.507
It is not money that
the UN denies us.

39:28.659 --> 39:31.194
I have the weapons.

39:31.228 --> 39:34.630
You'll get them shortly. Just give
me my daughter, take the money!

39:34.665 --> 39:36.266
I'll release them!

40:11.166 --> 40:14.235
This is what your
money has bought.

40:31.052 --> 40:33.921
A useful aid,

40:33.956 --> 40:38.093
for a father who will not
hear and does not listen.

40:38.127 --> 40:39.494
Kill him!

40:41.131 --> 40:42.164
Fucking kill them!

40:43.232 --> 40:44.232
All of them!

40:48.570 --> 40:49.737
Duck! Get down!

40:53.441 --> 40:54.608
Come on!

40:54.643 --> 40:56.577
Anyone hit?
No.

41:17.031 --> 41:18.199
Shit.

41:31.079 --> 41:32.179
Keep him alive!

41:32.214 --> 41:33.447
I'll do my best.

41:45.560 --> 41:46.527
Gotcha.

41:56.271 --> 41:57.705
Clare!

41:57.739 --> 41:58.739
Clare, to me!

42:05.181 --> 42:06.147
Clare!

42:09.518 --> 42:10.519
Get down to the ground!

42:16.660 --> 42:17.828
Fuck!

42:18.429 --> 42:19.595
Clare!

42:21.265 --> 42:22.298
Whoah, whoah, whoah!

42:23.600 --> 42:24.701
Just go back inside.

42:24.735 --> 42:26.102
Go back, it's all right.

42:26.137 --> 42:27.604
Stay inside. Fuck.

42:27.638 --> 42:28.905
What're you doin',
cocksucker?

42:28.939 --> 42:29.706
Where the fuck have you been?

42:29.740 --> 42:31.108
Saving your life!

42:32.210 --> 42:33.577
Clare! Stay down!

42:33.611 --> 42:34.645
Come on, Jacoub.

42:35.513 --> 42:36.647
Come on, buddy.

42:41.987 --> 42:42.720
Talk to me!

42:42.755 --> 42:44.122
You going for the girl?

42:44.156 --> 42:45.457
That's what
we came for, isn't it?

42:45.491 --> 42:46.558
Let's move!

42:46.593 --> 42:47.726
Comin' to ya!

42:51.231 --> 42:52.832
Cover me.

42:52.866 --> 42:54.233
<i>I'm going to</i>
<i>go in for the principal.</i>

42:56.603 --> 42:58.137
Clare, come here!

42:58.172 --> 42:59.171
Clare, move!

43:03.209 --> 43:04.243
Ahhh!

43:09.448 --> 43:11.349
Michael, the girl!

43:11.383 --> 43:12.416
Ahhh!

43:13.651 --> 43:14.818
Hang in there.

43:16.754 --> 43:18.121
Come on!

43:19.991 --> 43:21.158
Fuck.

43:25.563 --> 43:26.730
You get him?

43:27.665 --> 43:28.866
Oh, fuck!

43:51.455 --> 43:52.488
Shit.

43:54.758 --> 43:56.492
Did he get you?
Is he okay? Scott?

43:56.526 --> 43:57.660
Scott...

43:59.329 --> 44:00.562
Scott look here,
look here, look here!

44:00.597 --> 44:02.131
It's gonna be okay.

44:02.165 --> 44:03.799
Stay with me.

44:03.834 --> 44:04.900
Stay with me, Scott!

44:04.935 --> 44:05.968
Scott!

44:07.071 --> 44:08.237
Hey, Scott. Scott!

44:19.184 --> 44:20.218
What's that?

44:20.252 --> 44:21.986
It's uh, it's morphine.

44:22.020 --> 44:24.221
Oh, gimme. I love
that shit.

44:32.296 --> 44:33.363
Did we get the girl?

44:33.397 --> 44:34.397
No, not yet.

44:34.431 --> 44:36.298
Fuck.
Shit. He's bleeding out.

44:36.333 --> 44:38.133
You gotta get him to
a hospital, fast.

44:38.168 --> 44:39.568
- Come on, let's go!
- We're gonna patch you up.

44:42.105 --> 44:43.606
The fuck are you doing?

44:43.640 --> 44:45.641
I'm getting my daughter back,
and I'm taking that car.

44:45.676 --> 44:48.511
No! No.

44:48.545 --> 44:50.380
You need "a" car, and a better
car than this piece of shit

44:50.414 --> 44:53.216
if you have any hope of
getting across that desert.

44:53.250 --> 44:55.386
Now, my friends are
taking this,

44:55.420 --> 44:58.222
and you and I are taking one
of those Janjaweed technicals.

45:02.493 --> 45:04.661
Sinclair, take this gun in case
there's trouble along the way.

45:04.695 --> 45:05.929
You tell Grant what happened.

45:05.963 --> 45:07.864
Are you seriously going on?

45:07.898 --> 45:09.265
I have to find that
intel on Latif.

45:09.299 --> 45:11.166
Oh, like that's the reason
you're going, Mike.

45:11.201 --> 45:15.070
Come on. You're outgunned,
you got no backup, huh?

45:15.105 --> 45:17.305
How're you gonna even find her?
You don't know where the fuck to look.

45:17.340 --> 45:19.340
I do.

45:19.375 --> 45:20.942
What the fuck
is he saying?

45:20.976 --> 45:22.409
My village was near here.

45:22.444 --> 45:23.877
I can help you.

45:23.912 --> 45:26.246
All right. Let's all go.

45:26.281 --> 45:28.149
The morphine's kicking in.
I'm up for a road trip.

45:28.183 --> 45:31.085
No, you're going to a hospital
before you bleed to death.

45:31.120 --> 45:36.924
He, he's gonna die before
me. Stupid fucking Brit.

45:36.958 --> 45:39.426
Yo, there's tools in the back.
You go kick some ass.

45:39.460 --> 45:41.128
Thanks. Go.

45:43.198 --> 45:44.232
Drive.

45:54.510 --> 45:55.711
Let's do this.

